name: Abby
info: I was found as a puppy after I had escaped from a trap that had cut off the bottom parts of my back legs. After going through something so traumatic I’m a pretty shy girl but some I feel comfortable with you I love you the most. I like to sit close by to those that I trust and I really enjoy short walks to the beach! I support myself on my front legs but I can only walk for about 10 – 15 minutes before I need a break. I’d love a home with a garden or a shared green space that I can enjoy.
